description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, a mother in the UK will spend the next two and a half years of her life in prison for posting something “hateful” on social media. The UK, like so many other alleged liberal democracies across the West, has become a left-wing dictatorship. Also, the Democrat Party has spent $20 million hatching a plan to win back young male voters. We’ll take a look at the plan to see exactly how out of touch it is. And we have another super-viral entry in the ever-expanding genre of online videos where wives complain about their husbands.
